{"tid":817643,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好傷心 點解你要咁對我","createTime":"2018-09-13T13:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T11:13:57.000Z","uid":98334,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"20d05a93f348bea1cd907a60fc6e85e96610b542","tid":817643,"uid":98334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:34:26.000Z","msg":"男人都係一樣 口講幾愛你幾鍾意你都好<br />\n我錫你 唔捨得你洗咁多錢 知你無錢<br />\n從來都堅持AA 咩都AA<br />\n我愛你 你有咩唔想做嘅我都會幫你做<br />\n你唔開心唔高興我都盡我能力去氹你<br />\n點解你呃完我一次又一次<br />\n點解我明知係咁仲咁鍾意你<br />\n點解我放唔低你<br />\n點解我狠唔到心講分手<br />\n點解我覺得無論你點衰都好 只要你留係我身邊就夠<br />\n你未定性 我可以等你<br />\n你未玩夠 我可以等你<br />\n我唔想再拍拖喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我淨係想要你一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5f13ed4031a5bd2f56a5ad99c964419868a25b","tid":817643,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"傻"},{"pid":"c753ed96041929fad19b088c38c174181d6fcd1d","tid":817643,"uid":98334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a5f13ed4031a5bd2f56a5ad99c964419868a25b","tid":817643,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"傻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"我知我好傻好on9<br />\n但我真係好鍾意佢好愛佢<br />\n但果種幸福感真係得佢比到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4281156278635bf9fe66b363d03b4bc82689c997","tid":817643,"uid":148185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c753ed96041929fad19b088c38c174181d6fcd1d","tid":817643,"uid":98334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a5f13ed4031a5bd2f56a5ad99c964419868a25b","tid":817643,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"傻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"我知我好傻好on9<br />\n但我真係好鍾意佢好愛佢<br />\n但果種幸福感真係得佢比到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm